THE COMPANY HAS INTEREST RATE SWAP AGREEMENTS WITH THE SAME NOTIONAL AMOUNT AND MATURITY DATES AS THE $250.0 MILLION CORPORATE BOND MATURING AUGUST 15, 2006, WHEREBY THE COMPANY RECEIVES FIXED INTEREST

