PAYMENTS AT THE SAME RATE AS THE BOND AND PAYS VARIABLE INTEREST PAYMENTS BASED ON THE THREE-MONTH LIBOR PLUS A SPREAD. THE INTEREST RATES PAYABLE ON THESE

